<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Marvellous2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Marvellous,</orth> adv. (joined only to adjectives and adverbs), very, extraordinarily: <cit><quote>m. sweet music,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.3.19" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. III, 3, 19</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>m. little beholding,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 4.3.166" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 3, 166</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>m. merry,</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 4.3.59" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 3, 59</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a m. witty fellow,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 4.2.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado IV, 2, 27</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>m. well shot,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 4.1.132" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 1, 132</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. lll 4.2.158" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 158</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.586" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 586</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.1.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 1, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 4.1.26" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 26</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 2.73" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. II, 73</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.3.179" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 3, 179</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.4.30" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 4, 30</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.1.38" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 38</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.2.81" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 2, 81</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.255" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 255</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.2.150" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 2, 150</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 4.5.30" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. IV, 5, 30</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.5.230" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 5, 230</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.1.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 1, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.312" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 312</bibl>.
